                        <p class="is-size-6 ">Anthony Wilson, Arnadi Murtiyoso, Bernhard Jenny, I Gede Mahendra Darmawiguna, Putu Hendra Suputra, Thomas Chandler, Made Windu Antara Kesiman, Kadek Ananta Satriadi</p>
